statements: SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT campaign_name, target_audience, budget FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE budget > 1000;
SELECT campaign_id, total_impact FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE total_impact < 5000;
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE start_date >= '2023-01-01' AND end_date <= '2023-12-31';
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE budget > 5000 ORDER BY start_date DESC, total_impact ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT campaign_name, target_audience FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE budget BETWEEN 3000 AND 7000 ORDER BY campaign_name ASC;
SELECT campaign_id, start_date, end_date FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE total_impact > 1000 AND budget < 10000 ORDER BY end_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT campaign_name, total_impact FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE target_audience LIKE 'Students%' ORDER BY total_impact DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns_performance WHERE budget > 8000 AND (start_date < '2022-01-01' OR end_date > '2023-01-01') ORDER BY budget DESC, start_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM digital_campaign_performance;
SELECT campaign_name, total_participants FROM digital_campaign_performance;
SELECT campaign_name, total_engagements FROM digital_campaign_performance WHERE campaign_start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT campaign_name, total_participants, total_engagements FROM digital_campaign_performance ORDER BY total_engagements DESC;
SELECT campaign_name, total_engagements FROM digital_campaign_performance WHERE total_participants > 1000;
SELECT * FROM digital_campaign_performance;
SELECT campaign_name, campaign_start_date, total_participants FROM digital_campaign_performance ORDER BY campaign_start_date DESC;
SELECT campaign_name, total_engagements FROM digital_campaign_performance WHERE total_participants > 1000 ORDER BY total_engagements DESC;

SELECT campaign_name, engagement_type, engagement_date FROM digital_campaign_performance JOIN campaign_engagement_details ON digital_campaign_performance.campaign_id = campaign_engagement_details.campaign_id WHERE engagement_type = 'click';

SELECT campaign_name, engagement_type, engagement_date FROM digital_campaign_performance LEFT JOIN campaign_engagement_details ON digital_campaign_performance.campaign_id = campaign_engagement_details.campaign_id WHERE engagement_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM digital_literacy_campaigns;
SELECT metric_id, metrics_type, metric_value, timestamp FROM campaign_metrics;
SELECT * FROM participant_feedback WHERE campaign_id = 1;
SELECT campaign_id, participant_id, feedback_text, submission_date FROM participant_feedback;
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM digital_literacy_campaigns;
SELECT campaign_id, campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM digital_literacy_campaigns WHERE start_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM campaign_metrics WHERE metric_value > 100;
SELECT campaign_id, COUNT(*) AS total_feedback FROM participant_feedback GROUP BY campaign_id;
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns;
SELECT campaign_name, total_participants FROM digital_literacy_campaigns ORDER BY total_participants DESC;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender FROM campaign_participants WHERE participant_age > 20;
SELECT activity_name, activity_date FROM campaign_activities WHERE campaign_id = 1 ORDER BY activity_date DESC;
SELECT feedback_id, participant_id, feedback_description FROM campaign_feedback WHERE campaign_id = 2;
SELECT * FROM digital_literacy_campaigns;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM digital_literacy_campaigns WHERE total_participants > 50;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender FROM campaign_participants WHERE participant_age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 ORDER BY participant_age DESC;
SELECT activity_name, activity_date, activity_duration FROM campaign_activities WHERE activity_duration >= 60 ORDER BY activity_date ASC;

SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date, total_participants FROM digital_literacy_campaigns JOIN campaign_participants ON digital_literacy_campaigns.campaign_id = campaign_participants.campaign_id JOIN campaign_activities ON digital_literacy_campaigns.campaign_id = campaign_activities.campaign_id WHERE campaign_name LIKE '%Summer%' OR campaign_name LIKE '%Spring%' AND participant_age < 25 ORDER BY total_participants DESC;
SELECT * FROM digital_campaigns;
SELECT campaign_name, start_date, end_date FROM digital_campaigns WHERE budget > 5000;
SELECT campaign_id, impressions, clicks FROM campaign_metrics ORDER BY date_measured DESC;
SELECT influencer_name, social_media_platform FROM campaign_influencers WHERE campaign_id = '1234-5678-9012';
SELECT feedback_id, feedback, rating FROM campaign_feedback WHERE rating >= 4 ORDER BY feedback_id;
SELECT * FROM digital_campaigns WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT campaign_name, budget FROM digital_campaigns WHERE budget > 5000 ORDER BY budget DESC;

SELECT c.campaign_name, m.date_measured, m.impressions, m.clicks FROM digital_campaigns c JOIN campaign_metrics m ON c.campaign_id = m.campaign_id WHERE m.impressions >= 1000 ORDER BY m.impressions DESC;

SELECT d.*, c.influencer_name, c.social_media_platform FROM audience_demographics d JOIN campaign_influencers c ON d.campaign_id = c.campaign_id WHERE d.location = 'New York' AND c.social_media_platform = 'Instagram';
SELECT f.feedback_id, f.feedback, f.rating, c.campaign_name FROM campaign_feedback f JOIN digital_campaigns c ON f.campaign_id = c.campaign_id WHERE f.rating > 3 ORDER BY f.rating DESC;
